        <h2>Some facts about my good friend Tim Drake:</h2>
        <p> </p>
        <ol>
            <ul>
                <b>Hero Life</b>
                <ul>
                    <li>Timothy Jackson "Tim" Drake was the third sidekick to Batman as Robin before changing his hero name to Red Robin.</li>
                    <li>Following Batman's disappearance and assummed death, Tim goes on an adventure to find the man in the Red Robin (2009-2011) comic series.</li>
                </ul>
            </ul>
            <ul><b>Personal Life</b>
                <li>Tim dated Stephanie Brown, also known as Wondergirl but broke up. He is now in a relationship with an old classmate named Bernard Dowd.</li>
            </ul>
        </ol>
